data.description: SLEEK, MODERN, LUXURIOUS!  Want new construction but bored with the basic interior?? Look no further. You will not find a beauty like this.   Nearly $100,000 in UPGRADES!!  5-bedrooms, 3.5 baths w/formal, Office & an open concept from the family room to the kitchen. This home has natural and added recessed lighting that flows through. The beautiful, upgraded kitchen has walk-in pantry, great cabinet space, very nice countertops. LUXURIOUS  primary suite w/spa-like master bath & walk-in shower w/rain showers that rivals top 5 star resorts! his & her sinks (touch lighting mirrors), a private water room & a large walk-in closet. Upstairs 2 of the bedrooms sit away from the others giving some privacy. You then have a full bath & a large game room. Down the hallway sits the other 2 bedrooms & another full bath. Plenty of space. No back yard neighbors. The spacious garage has room for storage. Near Fort Bend County Fairgrounds, shopping, entertainment Grand Pkwy and HWY 69/59.
